		<title>CABINET HAS APPROVED THE NEW MINING CHARTER</title>
		<link>https://www.newspages.co.za/cabinet-has-approved-the-new-mining-charter/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 03 Oct 2018 07:26:04 +0000</pubDate>
